    },

    {
      "type": "section-header",
      "duration": 3,
      "transition": "slide-left",
      "data": {
        "heading": "The Problem",
        "subheading": "Agents produce data. Humans consume video."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "comparison",
      "duration": 6,
      "transition": "fade",
      "data": {
        "title": "Before vs After",
        "left": {
          "label": "Without Showrunner",
          "items": [
            "Raw tables pasted into chat",
            "Static screenshots of dashboards",
            "Walls of text nobody reads",
            "Manual PowerPoint assembly"
          ]
        },
        "right": {
          "label": "With Showrunner",
          "items": [
            "Animated MP4 with pacing",
            "Spring-eased chart animations",
            "Visual hierarchy and motion",
            "One JSON → one video"
          ]
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "type": "section-header",
      "duration": 3,
      "transition": "slide-left",
      "data": {
        "heading": "Step 1: Configure the MCP Server",
        "subheading": "Add it to your agent's MCP config — that's it."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "code-terminal",
      "duration": 8,
      "transition": "fade",
      "data": {
        "title": "Agent MCP Configuration",
        "shell": "~/.config/mcp.json",
        "lines": [
          { "kind": "comment", "text": "Add to your agent's MCP server config:" },
          { "kind": "blank" },
          { "kind": "prompt", "text": "<span class=\"keyword\">{</span>" },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "<span class=\"string\">\"mcpServers\"</span>: {" },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "  <span class=\"string\">\"video-engine\"</span>: {" },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "    <span class=\"string\">\"command\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"node\"</span>," },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "    <span class=\"string\">\"args\"</span>: [<span class=\"string\">\"dist/server.js\"</span>]," },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "    <span class=\"string\">\"transport\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"stdio\"</span>" },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "  }" },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "}" },
          { "kind": "prompt", "text": "<span class=\"keyword\">}</span>" },
          { "kind": "blank" },
          { "kind": "success", "text": "✓ MCP server registered — agent can now call video tools" }
        ]
      }
    },

    {
      "type": "section-header",
      "duration": 3,
      "transition": "slide-left",
      "data": {
        "heading": "Step 2: Ask the Agent",
        "subheading": "Describe what you want. The agent builds the storyboard."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "code-terminal",
      "duration": 10,
      "transition": "fade",
      "data": {
        "title": "Prompting the Agent to Generate a Video",
        "shell": "Copilot Chat",
        "lines": [
          { "kind": "comment", "text": "You type a prompt to the agent:" },
          { "kind": "blank" },
          { "kind": "prompt", "text": "Create a 30-second video summarizing our Q2 pipeline review." },
          { "kind": "prompt", "text": "Include a funnel chart, KPI scorecard, top risks, and action items." },
          { "kind": "prompt", "text": "Use the microsoft theme." },
          { "kind": "blank" },
          { "kind": "comment", "text": "The agent calls list_scene_types, builds a storyboard, then:" },
          { "kind": "blank" },
          { "kind": "highlight", "text": "→ Calling MCP tool: <span class=\"accent\">validate_storyboard</span>" },
          { "kind": "success", "text": "  ✓ Valid — 6 scenes, 32s duration, 960 frames" },
          { "kind": "blank" },
          { "kind": "highlight", "text": "→ Calling MCP tool: <span class=\"accent\">render_video</span>" },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "  ⠋ Rendering scene 1/6: title-card..." },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "  ⠙ Rendering scene 2/6: pipeline-funnel..." },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "  ⠹ Rendering scene 3/6: kpi-scorecard..." },
          { "kind": "output", "text": "  ⠸ Encoding H.264 MP4..." },
          { "kind": "blank" },
          { "kind": "success", "text": "  ✓ Video rendered: <span class=\"string\">/output/q2-pipeline-review.mp4</span>" },
          { "kind": "success", "text": "    Duration: <span class=\"number\">32s</span> | Frames: <span class=\"number\">960</span> | Size: <span class=\"number\">1.4 MB</span>" }
        ]
      }
    },

